  <div class="content">
    <h3>Overview</h3>

    <p>
      Islamic Studies              : Modern Standard Arabic. Focus on the development of speaking, listening, reading and writing skills, with an emphasis on the functional use of the language.          </p>

    <p class="catalog-terms">
      Terms:              Fall 2014          </p>

    <p class="catalog-instructors">
      Instructors:                        David Nancekivell (Fall)                  </p>

    
